public class Test01 {

public static void main(String[] args) {

{2, 4, 7},
{0, 8, 1},
{1, 4, 1},
{9, 3, 1},
};
System.out.println(Druga.najGlobina(m, p0));

int[][] p1 = {
{3, 5, 4},
{7, 9, 1},
{1, 6, 2},
{8, 8, 2},
{0, 2, 1},
};
System.out.println(Druga.najGlobina(m, p1));

int[][] p2 = {
{1, 8, 2},
{4, 6, 4},
{8, 6, 1},
{3, 4, 1},
{9, 3, 1},
{0, 5, 1},
};

{4, 8, 1},
{0, 9, 4},
{5, 6, 2},
{7, 3, 2},
{9, 6, 1},
};

{9, 4, 1},
};
System.out.println(Druga.najGlobina(m, p4));
